==English==
===Etymology===
< [[Old French]] ''versifier,'' learned borrowing from Latin ''versificāre'' < ''versus'' (see etym. for [[verse]]) + ''facere'' to make
===Transitive verb===
# to make or compose verses

===Intransitive verb===
#to tell in verse; deal with in verse form
#to turn ([[prose]]) into poetry; rewrite in verse form